# Data Quality {.smaller}

Data quality is the degree to which data is fit for its intended uses in operations, decision making and planning.

::: columns
::: {.column width="50%"}
-   Accuracy
-   Completeness
-   Consistency
-   Validity
-   Reliability
:::

::: {.column width="50%"}
-   Trustworthiness
-   Timeliness
-   Relevancy
-   Accessibility
-   Usability
:::
:::

